ReturnPolicy.Description:
All items including gifts, box and or pouch are to be returned. All items must be returned unworn, in same condition as received and postmarked within 30 days or less from time of receipt indicated on tracking. All items will include tracking.

If returning for any reason other than "changed your mind" photos must be included at time of return request. These photos should include complete condition of box, packing and item so a claim may be filed. Do not throw box, packing away unless instructed to do so as the post office sometimes requires it to complete the claim. NEVER dispose of the item(s). Per eBay guidelines, You must contact us before shipping back so we approve and know to expect the package return.
Thank You.

*Updated Security*  Effective: July 27, 2016 <center>
Multiple photos of the items are taken prior to sale and prior to shipping. I may even video the packaging so that we are both protected if an insurance claim becomes necessary. I am also able to positively identify any damages or differences to an item after shipment for this reason. This helps assure that you receive the item that I sent in the same condition as advertised, and helps assure that if there are any problems, that I receive insurance claim reimbursement by being able to prove that the item was sent in good condition. This is why I request that all items including original packaging materials and box also be returned with the item. The postal insurance requires these items, so I must be able to provide them. I may request photos from you if the item is received damaged so that I can get a head start on a claim while the item is being returned. Valuable items may contain a tamper-proof holographic "void if removed" security tag attached. If tag is present on item, please carefully inspect item upon receipt, notify me of any issues, and return with tag intact. Items with tag removed or tampered indicates your acceptance of item & are not eligible for return."  (Quixeller.com *reference recorded phone call - security measure has been approved by ebay on 7/25/16 by Michael* as part of their 30 day return policy implementation.)
